<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/39083.Mariano_Azuela"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1337630337p3/39083.jpg);'></div>
