<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer7710795444576147090">Mariano Azuela González was a Mexican author and physician, best known for his fictional stories of the Mexican Revolution of 1910. He wrote novels, works for theatre and literary criticism.</span>

